# Pixela Activity Tracker

A Python script to track activities using the [Pixela](https://pixe.la/) API. This tool helps you create and maintain a visual tracking graph of your activities (like cycling, in this example).

## 🌟 Features

- Create user accounts on Pixela
- Generate custom tracking graphs
- Log daily activities
- Secure API token handling
- Date-based activity tracking

## 📋 Prerequisites

- Python 3.6+
- `requests` library
- Pixela account ([Sign up here](https://pixe.la/))

